_sText:
An early release of a map I started working on today.

The time i've put in to de_industria (http://www.fpsbanana.com/studios/wips/view/12962) has made me weary, so I decided to release something quick and fun. I played it with some friends for an hour or so, and it plays pretty well, so I'm releasing it. Keep in mind this isn't a final version, I have some strange brush and lighting errors that I'll fix later.

Enjoy.
